{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "8be210ef-ed0e-436c-9a41-51c9533fe483", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/8be210ef-ed0e-436c-9a41-51c9533fe483@3.pkg/1772597551714/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597552414", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/8be210ef-ed0e-436c-9a41-51c9533fe483@3.pkg/1772597551714/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597552414"}, "identifier": "8be210ef-ed0e-436c-9a41-51c9533fe483", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>一审题干；二审设问；三审题肢。</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>A：中国共产党拥有执政权，要规范政府的行政权，故A说法错误；</p>\n\n<p>B：在更多领域更大范围实现“高效办成一件事”，说明要求政府转变政府职能，提高服务水平和效能，故B符合题意；</p>\n\n<p>C：“法无授权不可为”在材料中无体现，故C不符合题意；</p>\n\n<p>D：材料中无体现“政府科学民主决策”，故D不符合题意。</p>\n\n<p>故本题选B。</p>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<p style=\"margin-left:10.5000pt;\">（原创）2025年1月13日，国务院办公厅印发《“高效办成一件事”2025年度第一批重点事项清单》，要求进一步促进政务服务标准化、规范化、便利化，在更多领域更大范围实现“高效办成一件事”。这要求政府（&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;）</p>\n", "title": "（原创）2025年1月13日，国务院办公厅印发《“高效办成一件事”2025年度第一批重点事项清单》，要求进一步促进政务服务标准化、规范化、便利化，在更多领域更大范围实现“高效办成一件事”。这要求政府（     ）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["B"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/8be210ef-ed0e-436c-9a41-51c9533fe483@3.pkg/item.json?v=1754822140256", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "choice_type": "character", "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>规范政府执政权，提高政府执法能力</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>转变政府职能，提高服务水平和效能&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>法无授权不可为，建设人民满意的政府</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<p>推进政务公开，促进政府科学民主决策</p>\n"}], "prompt": "<p style=\"margin-left:10.5000pt;\">（原创）2025年1月13日，国务院办公厅印发《“高效办成一件事”2025年度第一批重点事项清单》，要求进一步促进政务服务标准化、规范化、便利化，在更多领域更大范围实现“高效办成一件事”。这要求政府（&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;）</p>\n", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878"}, "source": {"container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "tags": ["$M002000000", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "ff8080814371757b014390fcdce504bd", "5136342960", "44bec67a-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "$RE0000", "$M003002000", "5036342749", "$RE0200", "6a74973a-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "$RE0201", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "ff8080814371757b014390fcdce504bd", "5136342960", "44bec67a-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "6a74973a-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5"], "status": "ONLINE", "is_publish": false, "id": "8be210ef-ed0e-436c-9a41-51c9533fe483", "global_title": {"zh-CN": "（原创）2025年1月13日，国务院办公厅印发《“高效办成一件事”2025年度第一批重点事项清单》，要求进一步促进政务服务标准化、规范化、便利化，在更多领域更大范围实现“高效办成